  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Provide Legal Support to Refugees in Athens</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ELIL has been running a successful legal assistance programme on Lesvos for four years and recently launched a new project on Samos. We are now further expanding our operations to meet the significant need for legal assistance for refugees on the Greek mainland. In light of recent events and of the increasingly strict asylum framework being imposed in Europe, guaranteeing meaningful access to legal assistance is more important than ever. Donations are tax deductible in the UK and US.</narrative>
  </description>
